Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.96,0:01:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会知道这里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.17,0:01:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在拼命找你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.82,0:01:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你突然间就不见了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.96,0:01:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没资格说别人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.54,0:01:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左慈君也很担心你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.64,0:01:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.33,0:01:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明在洛阳遇到了左慈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.48,0:01:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不记得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.40,0:01:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 完全不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.80,0:02:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对我说了谎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.78,0:02:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 在那之后也...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.00,0:02:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直都在和左慈见面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.12,0:02:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和左慈两个人一直在欺骗和嘲笑我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.21,0:02:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 没有这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.83,0:02:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确 左慈君让我对你说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.32,0:02:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 我们也有瞒着你见面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.67,0:02:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 这都是为了你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.25,0:02:26.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说是为了我？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.97,0:02:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第九话 多算胜 少算则不胜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.86,0:02:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.01,0:02:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和左慈君还有我在过去的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.20,0:02:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这样吕蒙才会害怕我恢复过去的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.49,0:02:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左慈君希望我能够隐瞒我们见面的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.77,0:02:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他也这么说过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.97,0:02:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是我恢复了记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.48,0:02:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也不会再交往了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.14,0:02:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在除了吕蒙以外
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.36,0:03:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的心里已经无法容纳任何人了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么他一直都不现身
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.19,0:03:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左慈君一直在为了弄清楚我还活着的谜团而奔波
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他说在解开谜团之前是不会去见吕蒙的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.70,0:03:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙至少也应该跟我说一声
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.77,0:03:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.32,0:03:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人也许在这方面很要面子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.14,0:03:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不坦率呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.94,0:03:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吕蒙也正是喜欢他这点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.55,0:03:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突...突然间说什么啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.59,0:03:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.84,0:03:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左慈君对你保密是不想让你担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.96,0:03:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明告诉过他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.29,0:03:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不在乎自己活下来的理由了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.56,0:03:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在乎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.07,0:03:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为对于现在的我已经不需要过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.56,0:03:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.19,0:04:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一起生活的时光更为宝贵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.16,0:04:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.01,0:04:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了荒废的洛阳高校之后 我就全明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.51,0:04:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里黑暗冰冷 令人害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.45,0:04:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吕蒙 和你一起的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.17,0:04:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我就不被过去束缚而活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.38,0:04:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.69,0:04:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是无论如何都在意我和左慈君的关系的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.93,0:04:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吕蒙应该不愿意和我一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.94,0:04:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.47,0:04:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果被你继续厌恶下去的话 我会受不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.78,0:04:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 就此告别了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.50,0:04:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.87,0:04:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会再怀疑你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.70,0:05:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意相信我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.68,0:05:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.47,0:05:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后我们会一直在一起的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.48,0:05:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吕布小姐她？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.90,0:05:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 小刘是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.74,0:05:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的 小刘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.92,0:05:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这么哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.63,0:05:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 大家没有生命危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.79,0:05:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.00,0:05:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生了什么事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.79,0:05:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天我接到了吕布小姐的邀请
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.64,0:05:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了游乐园 一起进了鬼城
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.65,0:05:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吕布小姐...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.43,0:05:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.24,0:05:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难以启齿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.48,0:05:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么可能会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.73,0:06:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那之后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.93,0:06:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有谁进入了我的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.61,0:06:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...因为我...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.05,0:06:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害了关羽姐她们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.72,0:06:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有谁进入了体内...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.62,0:06:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...从什么时候开始的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.70,0:06:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仲谋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.34,0:06:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧 公瑾哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.59,0:06:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和吕布见面的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.17,0:06:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仲谋的样子很明显有些异常
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.48,0:06:43.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她到底在害怕什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.74,0:06:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公瑾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.88,0:06:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去找小布
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.70,0:06:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.87,0:06:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小陆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.69,0:06:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.19,0:06:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军师 陆逊伯言
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.20,0:07:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吕布奉先已经不在蒙姐的房间里了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.19,0:07:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且吕布也不过是被操控了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.08,0:07:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被操控...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.48,0:07:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被谁？陆逊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.72,0:07:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左慈元放
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.39,0:07:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小左慈？为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.91,0:07:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,策殿所说的左慈 既是左慈又不是左慈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.05,0:07:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙的真名是王允子师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.71,0:07:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了打倒董卓仲颖自称是左慈元放而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.03,0:07:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...希望可以简单地说明一下...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.19,0:07:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了我们认识的左慈之外
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.60,0:07:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有另一位名为左慈元放的斗士存在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.65,0:07:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.72,0:07:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.86,0:07:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:07:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士孙瑞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.98,0:08:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩戴那枚勾玉 恢复王允身份还太早
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.51,0:08:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛阳的董卓和吕布同归于尽的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.62,0:08:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左慈元放这个伪名的存在还有什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.41,0:08:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.52,0:08:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三国时代的王允子师在用连环计灭掉董卓之后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.69,0:08:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死在了董卓手下的逆贼手上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.35,0:08:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王允在此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.67,0:08:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.54,0:08:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才要恢复王允的身份 完成他未完成的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.33,0:08:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.42,0:08:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 左慈元放这个伪名并不只是为了骗过董卓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.37,0:08:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.15,0:08:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三国时代的左慈元放拥有幻术
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.50,0:08:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预言了曹操孟德之死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.54,0:08:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土鼠随金虎 奸雄一旦休
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.09,0:09:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是让我去预言许昌曹操的死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.12,0:09:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并非如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主作为左慈元放应该做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.38,0:09:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了能够见到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.52,0:09:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有朝一日将继承勾玉现身于关东的幻师左慈元放
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.71,0:09:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后也是为了毁灭他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.75,0:09:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.68,0:09:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.06,0:09:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关节技高手 无敌的小蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.43,0:09:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格斗游戏的水平也就不过如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.79,0:09:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天只是状态不好而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.50,0:09:44.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平时会更...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.38,0:09:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是 过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.67,0:09:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起拍照吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.76,0:09:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对这种东西...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.34,0:09:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得无聊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.68,0:09:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不...不是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.46,0:10:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.67,0:10:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.18,0:10:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不坦率啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.76,0:10:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑一笑 笑一笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.39,0:10:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.62,0:10:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然擅作主张在别人的手机上贴上这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.50,0:10:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 你不喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.49,0:10:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁...谁也没这么说过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.13,0:10:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就取下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.68,0:10:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总...总之 我今天很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.88,0:10:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.49,0:10:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说一遍好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.18,0:10:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨...笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.35,0:10:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天很开心 明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.46,0:10:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.74,0:10:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.57,0:10:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.28,0:10:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左慈元放
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.18,0:10:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曹操已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.30,0:11:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今你才慢吞吞地出来要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.71,0:11:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吕蒙子明
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.79,0:11:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想得到沉睡在她体内的龙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.69,0:11:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.12,0:11:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很悲伤的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.20,0:11:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤独 绝望 以及怨恨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.99,0:11:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能看到这些东西而一路走过来的人类的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.78,0:11:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我说这些 想让我怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.99,0:11:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会和我一起行动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.95,0:11:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吗？愚蠢 你以为你是预言家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.16,0:11:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以唤醒你最重要的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.51,0:11:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的过去...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.34,0:12:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会...不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.64,0:12:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吕布奉先...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.60,0:12:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道真的可以起死回生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.10,0:12:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.48,0:12:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.66,0:12:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.00,0:12:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然唤醒了她的身体 可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要唤醒她的记忆 还需要一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.92,0:12:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.63,0:12:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吕布的记忆不是还未...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.32,0:12:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并没有完全的苏醒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.62,0:12:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么她为什么在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.71,0:13:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱使现在吕布行动的是她作为斗士的本能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.43,0:13:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.53,0:13:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作点 吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.73,0:13:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人畏惧的斗士的本能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.30,0:13:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使尚未恢复记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.60,0:13:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吕布的本能令她不由自主地寻求敌人和战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.73,0:13:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来唤醒她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.43,0:13:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.10,0:13:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她和吕蒙相见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.69,0:13:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见吕蒙子明？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.27,0:13:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在过去 吕蒙曾经倾听过吕布的心声
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吕布竟然以这样的形式复活了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.02,0:13:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吕蒙的话 应该无法对她置之不理
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.65,0:13:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 吕布就能恢复记忆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.05,0:13:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这种可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.73,0:13:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吕布和吕蒙...都是斗士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.21,0:13:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 吕布并没有恢复记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.57,0:14:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不惜以身试险去见她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.98,0:14:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想揭示她和我过去的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.60,0:14:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然对于吕布而言 作为斗士而活的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.48,0:14:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是可憎的过去的束缚而已吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.78,0:14:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个怪物在笑什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.67,0:14:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你打算吃掉那只蝴蝶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.89,0:14:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为怪物的饲料倒是正合适呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.24,0:15:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.98,0:15:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啊 不吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.76,0:15:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得人家想对你亲切一点的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.14,0:15:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个孩子会使用奇怪的能力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.85,0:15:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次高年级的学生吃了大苦头就是因为这个原因吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.80,0:15:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什...什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.82,0:15:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要看这边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.11,0:15:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚去那边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.61,0:15:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.81,0:15:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.51,0:15:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点滚出去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.31,0:15:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少和我们呼吸同样的空气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.00,0:15:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人火大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.37,0:15:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.77,0:15:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活该
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.10,0:15:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点滚开 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.20,0:16:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.06,0:16:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手不由自主的...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼 好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.23,0:16:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王允
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.18,0:16:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要让我孤单一人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.81,0:16:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里都不要去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.28,0:16:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要实现我的愿望啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.99,0:16:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是幻术师 左慈元放
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.95,0:17:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 那个真的小左慈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.56,0:17:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用小布对小刘施了魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.31,0:17:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,致使成都的众人发生了争斗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.52,0:17:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你终于能理解了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.77,0:17:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 理解了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.47,0:17:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罪魁祸首是那个魔女左慈对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.15,0:17:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.65,0:17:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.33,0:17:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.14,0:17:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还用问吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.88,0:17:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是魔法师小左慈那里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.18,0:17:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能原谅她的罪恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.05,0:17:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对要让她停手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.57,0:17:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道她在哪里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.19,0:17:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小陆你不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.85,0:17:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么可能会知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.54,0:17:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.99,0:17:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些已经是我千辛万苦才收集到的情报啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.45,0:17:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仲谋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吕布...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.84,0:18:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是我恢复了记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.29,0:18:29.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也不会再交往了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.66,0:18:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在除了吕蒙以外
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.86,0:18:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的心里已经无法容纳任何人了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.19,0:18:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为对于现在的我已经不需要过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.85,0:18:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.12,0:18:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一起生活的时光更为宝贵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.85,0:18:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意相信我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.55,0:18:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.49,0:19:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左慈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.15,0:19:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.94,0:19:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.07,0:19:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这正是龙力量的源泉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.71,0:19:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吕布 你果然是在欺骗我 把我当作笑料
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.58,0:19:43.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那时候曾说过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.57,0:19:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使无法反抗勾玉所指引的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.71,0:19:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是一直战斗至今的我自己所选择的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.36,0:19:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.40,0:19:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了自己 凭借自己的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.64,0:20:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我也为了自己 凭借自己的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.37,0:20:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将你...打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.96,0:20:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让你...伤害这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.64,0:20:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蒙？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.88,0:21:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吕蒙子明 你不会被允许以自己的意志而活
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.84,0:21:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.26,0:21:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是龙所寄宿的斗士
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.17,0:23:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陆逊小姐 初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.12,0:23:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是孙权仲谋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.21,0:23:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,策殿居然会有这样的妹妹真是难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.07,0:23:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起策殿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.32,0:23:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又笨 任性 没毅力 又能吃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.69,0:23:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个无药可救的当家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.14,0:23:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.70,0:23:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是真正的主角啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.48,0:23:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 陆逊小姐是因为登场太晚而在生气而已
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.99,0:23:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十话 上兵伐谋
